SENTENCE but ,  there are questions about this too .
SENTENCE we know that bananas can be a staple food that can support large populations ,  as they did in uganda in the more recent past .
SENTENCE if bananas were grown thousands of years ago ,  why don't we see evidence of large populations thriving in the area earlier ?
SENTENCE so ,  we are left with this mystery .
SENTENCE we have what appears to be strong biological evidence that bananas were being cultivated in uganda as early as 5 ,     years ago .
SENTENCE but we are missing other kinds of evidence that would conclusively prove that this is so .
SENTENCE clearly ,  more research needs to be done .
SENTENCE perhaps by some new scholars from this university ?
SENTENCE at least give it some thought .
